OL,3,CTyne Tunnel tolls increase from today
OL,5,FDrivers have to pay more to use the
OL,6,FTyne Tunnel from today.
OL,8,FThe increase in the tunnel toll means
OL,9,Fa single trip through the crossing is
OL,10,Fnow #2.40 for cars and #4.80 for HGVs,
OL,11,FLGVs, vans or buses over 3.5 tonnes -
OL,12,Fa rise of 9%.
OL,14,FHowever, it means toll charges have
OL,15,Frisen by up to 26% in just over a year.
OL,17,FOn 1 May 2023, the cost for cars rose
OL,18,Ffrom #1.90 to #2.20 and from #3.90 to
OL,19,F#4.40 for HGVs.
