OL,3,CTyne Tunnel tolls increase from today
OL,5,FIt comes as major roadworks are
OL,6,Funderway on the Tyne Bridge, with lane
OL,7,Fclosures causing severe disruption for
OL,8,Fmotorists.
OL,10,FTT2, which operates the tunnel, said
OL,11,Fthe increase is necessary to cover the
OL,12,Frunning and maintenance costs, as well
OL,13,Fas to repay the costs of the
OL,14,Fconstruction of the second Tyne Tunnel.
OL,16,FPre-Paid Account holders will continue
OL,17,Fto receive a 10% discount on their
OL,18,Fjourney.
